bhp grille with a mini-SUV attached|date=2019-09-25|website=Top Gear|language=en|access-date=2019-11-20}}</ref>\n|n/a\n|n/a\n|[[List of Volkswagen Group petrol engines#2.5 I5 20v TFSI .28Audi TTRS.2C RS3.2C RSQ3 .26 quattro Concept.29|2,480 cc I5 20v TFSI]]\n|{{convert|294|kW|PS bhp|0|abbr=on}}\n|4.5 sec.\n|155&nbsp;mph\n\n(250&nbsp;km/h)\n|5 dr, 5 seat [[crossover (automobile)|Crossover]]\n\n\n\n5 dr, 4 seat [[crossover (automobile)|Crossover]]\n\n(Sportback)<br />\n|\n 1,790 kg\n\n 1,775 kg\n|2020\n|[[File:Audi RS Q3 F3 IMG 2071.jpg|alt=|200x200px]]\n|-\n|'''[[Audi A7#Second generation (Type 4K8; 2018\u2013present)|Audi ''RS 7'']]'''\n|[[Volkswagen Group MLB platform|MLB Evo]]\n| C8\n|[[List of Volkswagen Group petrol engines#4.0 TFSI|3,993 cc V8 TFSI]]\n|{{convert|441|kW|PS bhp|0|abbr=on}}\n|3.6 sec.\n|190&nbsp;mph\n(305&nbsp;km/h)\n|5 dr, 4 seat [[fastback|Sportback (fastback)]]\n|\n 2,140 kg\n|2020\n|[[File:Audi RS7 C8 at IAA 2019 IMG 0307.jpg|200px]]\n|-\n|'''[[Audi RS 6|Audi ''RS 6'' Avant]]'''\n|[[Volkswagen Group MLB platform|MLB Evo]]\n|C8\n|[[List of Volkswagen Group petrol engines#4.0 TFSI|3,993 cc V8 TFSI]]\n|{{convert|441|kW|PS bhp|0|abbr=on}}\n|3.6 sec.\n|190&nbsp;mph\n(305&nbsp;km/h)\n|5 dr, 5 seat [[station wagon|Avant (estate/wagon)]]\n|\n 2,150 kg\n|2020\n|[[File:Audi RS6 Avant C8 at IAA 2019 IMG 0194.jpg|alt=|200x200px]]\n|-\n|[[Audi S8|'''Audi ''S8''''']]\n|[[Volkswagen Group MLB platform|MLB Evo]]\n|D5\n|[[List of Volkswagen Group petrol engines#4.0 TFSI|3,993 cc V8 TFSI]]\n|{{convert|420|kW|PS bhp|0|abbr=on}}\n|3.8 sec.\n|155&nbsp;mph\n(250&nbsp;km/h)\n|4 dr, 5 seat [[sedan (automobile)|Saloon (sedan)]]\n|\n 2,305 kg\n|2020\n|\n|-\n|'''[[Audi Q8#SQ8 (2019-)|Audi ''SQ8'']]'''||[[Volkswagen Group MLB platform|MLB]]|| ||[[List of Volkswagen Group diesel engines#4.0 V8 TDI 31--320kW|3,956 cc V8 TDI]]||{{convert|320|kW|PS bhp|0|abbr=on}}||4.8 sec.\n|155&nbsp;mph\n\n(250&nbsp;km/h)\n|5 dr, 5 seat [[crossover (automobile)|Crossover]]\n|\n 2,440\u00a0