8 Audi RS 4 Avant Front.jpg|200px]]\n|-\n|'''[[Audi A5#RS5 (2010\u2013)|Audi ''RS 5'']]'''\n|[[Volkswagen Group MLB platform|MLB Evo]]||F5||[[list of Volkswagen Group petrol engines#CAKA|2,894 cc V6 TFSI]]||{{convert|331|kW|PS bhp|0|abbr=on}}||3.9 sec.\n|174&nbsp;mph\n(280&nbsp;km/h)\n|2 dr, 4 seat mid-size [[Coup\u00e9]]\n\n<br>5 dr, 4 seat [[fastback|Sportback (fastback)]]\n|\n 1,782\u00a0kg\n\n 1,817\u00a0kg\n|2019\n|| [[File:Audi RS5 Coupe IMG 0728.jpg|200px]]<br>[[File:Classic Days 2019, Berlin (CDB90074).jpg|200px]]\n|-\n|'''[[Audi S5|Audi ''S5'']]'''||[[Volkswagen Group MLB platform|MLB Evo]]||F5||[[List of Volkswagen Group diesel engines#4.0%20V8%20TDI%2031--320kW|2,967 cc V6 TDI]]\n[[List of Volkswagen Group petrol engines#3.0/2.9 V6 24v TFSI (EA839)|2,995 cc V6 TFSI]]\n|{{convert|255|kW|PS bhp|0|abbr=on}}||4.8 sec.\n(coupe)\n\n4.9 sec.\n\n(sportback)\n\n5.1 sec.\n\n(cabriolet)\n|155&nbsp;mph\n(250&nbsp;km/h)\n|2 dr, 4 seat mid-size [[Coup\u00e9]]\n\n<br>5 dr, 4 seat [[fastback|Sportback (fastback)]]\n\n<br>2 dr, 4 seat mid-size [[Cabriolet]]\n|\n 1,835\u00a0kg\n\n 1,870\u202fkg\n\n 1,915 kg\n|2019\n<br />\n|[[File:2018 Audi S5 TFSi Quattro Automatic 3.0 Front.jpg|200px]]<br>[[File:2018 Audi S5 TFSi Quattro Automatic 3.0 Front (1).jpg|200px]]<br>[[File:2017 Audi S5 TFSi Quattro Automatic 3.0.jpg|200px]]\n|-\n|'''[[Audi TT#TTS|Audi ''TTS'']]'''||[[Volkswagen Group MQB platform|MQB]]||8S||[[List of Volkswagen Group petrol engines#EA888 2.0 litre turbo|1,984 cc I4 TFSI]]||{{convert|228|kW|PS bhp|0|abbr=on}}||4.5 sec. (coupe)<br> 4.8 sec. (roadster)\n|155&nbsp;mph\n(250&nbsp;km/h)\n| 2 dr 2 seat compact [[Coup\u00e9]]\n<br>{{nowrap|2 dr, 2 seat compact<br>[[Roadster (automobile)|Roadster]] ([[convertible (car)|convertible]])}}\n|\n 1,480\u202fkg\n\n 1,570 kg\n|2019||[[File:2016 Audi TTS TFSi Quattro S-A 2.0 Front.jpg|200px]]<br/>[[File:Audi_TTS_-_Mondial_de_l%27Automobile_de_Paris_2014_-_002.jpg|200px]]\n|-\n|'''[[Audi_TT#TT_RS_2|Audi ''TT RS'']]'''||[[Volkswag